            <h2>What floor drain cleaning actually solves</h2>
            <p>Floor drains in commercial kitchens see grease that residential drains never deal with, plus mop water, food debris, and detergent. The line behind the drain fouls slowly until the day a slow drain becomes a stop-work problem.</p><p>Honest Drain cabling plus periodic jetting cleans the inside of the pipe so the drain works at capacity, not just at minimum flow. After-hours service keeps the cleaning out of the operator's open hours.</p>
